Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.89,0:24:31.88,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本故事純屬虛構，與現實中任何人物、團體或事件無任何關連
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.88,0:24:33.88,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.56,0:02:23.19,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已經安排好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.79,0:02:24.66,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.03,0:02:26.18,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰開…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.21,0:02:29.03,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出去嗎，小彼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.05,0:02:33.29,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.85,0:02:36.51,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逼不及待要去把第一個月的工資花光光啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:37.93,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然不是全花光！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.16,0:02:42.39,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要給家裡匯錢  好不容易自己也有工資了，還想一起寄一份禮物什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.40,0:02:43.24,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:45.12,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有給自己的獎勵吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:46.27,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:51.14,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛開始的一個月是實習期，白打工了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.51,0:02:52.55,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.57,0:02:54.76,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩，但是嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.16,0:03:00.58,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說經常遲發工資，而且一般是發軍票的說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:03.53,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡，辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.26,0:03:07.74,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.78,0:03:13.78,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到真的拿到錢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.05,0:03:15.27,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然咯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.39,0:03:17.74,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此我們部隊才做副業…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.38,0:03:22.15,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方，那個那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.16,0:03:25.35,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天城裡開設集市了，是第一次對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.83,0:03:31.07,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛拿到第一份工資又剛好是第一次休假，都是第一次，\N小彼很興奮吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.21,0:03:34.09,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記工作，好好放鬆一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.92,0:03:35.55,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:45.20,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:56.76,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了別讓彼方起疑心嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.10,0:04:04.63,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但根據一般情況考慮，這種連補給都經常延遲的邊境，\n怎可能會發工資了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:13.38,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但彼方竟然就這麼相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.76,0:04:16.59,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,率真是彼方的優點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:17.49,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.60,0:04:22.97,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和立刻懷疑錢的出處的你們不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.98,0:04:24.20,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.32,0:04:29.90,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.13,0:04:34.24,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們也忘記工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.43,0:04:43.69,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.69,0:04:44.48,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.79,0:04:47.09,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，有一個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:49.57,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再降價可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.58,0:04:57.55,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，看得著迷了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.57,0:05:11.31,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來已經準備好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:13.94,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩，一切沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:17.49,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊有問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:22.33,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便提個建議，接受嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.11,0:05:25.80,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請詳細說說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.29,0:05:27.59,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.82,0:05:32.35,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！這件也很可愛呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.99,0:05:51.32,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你們啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.81,0:05:54.17,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西的賣主
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.68,0:06:04.32,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貨品還滿意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.60,0:06:05.75,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:08.51,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.95,0:06:11.21,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.67,0:06:13.54,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊拉，是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:18.46,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這點貨物，沙漠中運輸又難還很費時
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:22.70,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算一算，有點超出預算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.03,0:06:23.74,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.83,0:06:26.07,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是不打折原則的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:28.85,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,價格也是、味道也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:32.53,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打折什麼的就不提了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.59,0:06:37.11,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貨我們全收下了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.17,0:06:38.16,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.56,0:06:46.13,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢開槍的試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:49.62,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心這傢伙走火
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.62,0:06:52.98,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次在那帽子主人的頭上開個洞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.98,0:06:54.87,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.38,0:06:59.00,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:06.72,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看低我們的懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:09.94,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安，小夥子們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.75,0:07:42.21,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:51.28,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你們也是那些傢伙的同夥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:07:57.55,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美潮！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:06.61,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，車子！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:08.78,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.90,0:08:10.80,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.14,0:08:13.18,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，給頭領的禮物…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:14.98,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保住小命再說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.34,0:08:16.25,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.50,0:08:19.14,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可什麼都不知道，那麼危險的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:21.85,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也不來這鬼地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:27.82,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.24,0:08:29.09,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.00,0:08:33.53,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了可以了，大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:37.80,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捏了一把汗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.17,0:08:41.01,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來總算瞞混過關了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:43.96,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝合作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.97,0:08:48.42,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼沒什麼，要是中央的黑手黨跑到這裡來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:50.25,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的買賣也都別想做了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.51,0:08:53.24,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相互助，是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:59.11,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，算上這個演戲的份，自然價錢上會讓步一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:03.37,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊拉，討厭，米克羅先生真會開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.38,0:09:07.34,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不，這可不是玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.71,0:09:10.07,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是商業世界對不？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.31,0:09:13.27,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份錢我來承擔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:17.91,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面的車子，是你們砸壞的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.88,0:09:20.73,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:22.07,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.59,0:09:27.69,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩？不對啊，看來是有人幫我們砸了車子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:33.52,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車裡面，有很多集市上買的戰利品
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.16,0:09:38.42,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以回收的形式買下，利益平分怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.15,0:09:43.11,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買賣成交
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.44,0:09:44.16,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.43,0:09:49.23,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於不用演戲了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.16,0:09:52.10,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，有點驚訝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:53.02,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:57.77,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為梨旺前輩完全進入狀態了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.44,0:09:59.47,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私制這些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:02.52,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曝光了的話，不是上軍事法庭就算完的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:08.39,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,違犯專賣法和稅法，最壞是叛國罪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.83,0:10:12.61,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，雖是從前輩手上接下來的副業
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:15.19,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨旺可是一次都沒反對過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:17.50,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有點意外
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:27.67,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為剛開始的時候太驚訝了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.05,0:10:34.42,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當知道母親喜歡的卡魯巴度斯竟然是在城砦被造出來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:38.76,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那，你被編配到這個部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.13,0:10:42.28,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定也是受你母親的指引呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.21,0:11:02.93,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.72,0:11:12.26,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弓奈姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.05,0:11:15.49,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了，快看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:18.79,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好看，清哉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.93,0:11:30.10,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美潮，今天是第一次出席儀式呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.47,0:11:33.97,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神父也在這，所以，今天就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:34.87,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.53,0:11:39.79,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要給姐姐添麻煩，美潮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:42.10,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不好的，梳個頭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.11,0:11:44.03,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行，絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:47.42,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不行，你不是整天碎碎念要我乾淨什麼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.67,0:11:49.01,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清哉你煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:55.96,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以這樣，美潮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.67,0:12:00.46,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美潮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.27,0:12:08.08,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10圓25錢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:13.36,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意點，小妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.80,0:12:16.77,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起，剛才有點入迷了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.39,0:12:21.01,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心看…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:21.71,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有問題的是那些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.03,0:12:24.79,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來發現我們的交易
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.87,0:12:30.71,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:34.11,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  重要的是，奈緒美小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.20,0:12:36.62,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.75,0:12:41.00,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次錢包裡有能買下它的錢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.13,0:12:44.16,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只要說一聲「請給我這個」，可就真能買下來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.30,0:12:50.00,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，如果現在有人要和你搶買這個海豚的話，你怎麼辦呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:53.52,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？有人也說要買嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.70,0:12:56.24,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是，我只是打個比方而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:13:00.72,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…我的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:05.00,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，我會說海豚是會吃人的很可怕的動物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:06.06,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他死了這條心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.18,0:13:09.24,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩？…啊！你是天才！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.23,0:13:15.35,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  那個海豚我會一直給你留著，直到你說不要為止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.41,0:13:16.95,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心糾結吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.59,0:13:21.87,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，那我先給大家買禮物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:33.13,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…老爸，老媽，爺爺，奶奶… 華倫的爺爺和奶奶，曾祖母
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.74,0:13:35.94,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有隔壁的菜菜代婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.26,0:13:42.54,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害，什麼都有賣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.66,0:13:43.53,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.31,0:13:45.72,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.15,0:13:50.78,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩？美潮？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:52.95,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在買什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:56.10,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是在找個盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.11,0:13:56.85,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盒子？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.28,0:14:00.58,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣子的，有在哪裡見過嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.42,0:14:04.52,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.10,0:14:10.37,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找東西的話，我幫你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.82,0:14:13.20,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方，你在幹嘛呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.06,0:14:16.55,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我麼？在選禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.74,0:14:20.53,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找些很棒的東西當成禮物送給家鄉的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.89,0:14:22.44,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不算是很急…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.45,0:14:22.95,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:36.07,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美潮今天怎麼了？…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:42.29,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.85,0:14:44.86,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩，很漂亮的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:47.27,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}衣服上的字: Yoroshiku，即「請」的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:47.27,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個也很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.19,0:14:52.57,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弓奈…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.69,0:14:55.31,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個，彼方…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.94,0:14:58.02,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有見到美潮嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.32,0:15:02.01,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盒子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.28,0:15:04.79,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩，說是很重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.68,0:15:06.94,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:13.87,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她母親去世的時候，家財全部落入他人之手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.53,0:15:20.02,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說就是那個時候，一起被帶走的一個她媽媽的細竹筐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:24.23,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個孩子每到集市開張的時候，總想著還有什麼可能性…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.16,0:15:29.44,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了不該說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.56,0:15:33.67,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為昨天第一次領到薪水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:36.97,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以對她說要給家人寄禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:38.50,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:44.70,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在，我，我們就是美潮的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.07,0:15:49.08,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是這樣美潮還是羨慕別人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.90,0:15:53.53,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也全是我沒有盡力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.66,0:16:07.66,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.78,0:16:11.01,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽的盒子和美潮哪個最重要？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.02,0:16:12.97,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.30,0:16:19.17,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.61,0:16:27.67,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美潮…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:38.73,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美潮！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.42,0:16:46.17,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來看啊，特雷茲的特產爆竹！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.18,0:16:48.24,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,響聲多美啊  要一個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.12,0:16:57.44,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐… 弓奈姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.98,0:16:59.29,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.30,0:17:00.20,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美潮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:08.62,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的車！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:17.84,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是弓奈姐姐，不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.92,0:17:26.82,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐… 弓奈姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.18,0:17:28.96,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.97,0:17:30.05,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.87,0:17:35.44,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:36.33,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:41.81,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩？怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.09,0:17:45.64,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個車子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.87,0:17:47.83,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是奈緒美小姐的麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.11,0:17:49.94,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是你們？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.11,0:17:52.31,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.48,0:17:56.39,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有150圓，就當是賠償…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.29,0:17:59.74,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈… 你們真是幫了我大忙啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:02.01,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個收起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.28,0:18:05.06,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為賠償這裡的已經足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:11.58,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒美小姐，那個！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:19.95,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是意為「美麗的稻穗」的伊蒂亞文字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.04,0:18:21.68,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個刻上印章的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.69,0:18:27.04,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子一定會像豐收的田地一樣，過上幸福的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.01,0:18:32.24,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美穗，你得到一個好名字了呢，太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.02,0:18:40.63,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到美潮了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.09,0:18:47.69,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了成為她的家人我自問已經竭盡我所能…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.05,0:18:50.55,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但看來我做的還不夠呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.80,0:18:54.73,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，你已經很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.12,0:19:00.08,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美潮！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.39,0:19:07.74,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，找到盒子了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.35,0:19:09.85,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好珍惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.34,0:19:13.10,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可替代的對媽媽的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.11,0:19:14.03,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:19.35,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望弓奈姐姐能收下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:32.54,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美潮是失去家人，被教會收留的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.35,0:19:38.62,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先是她父親應徵上戰場至今未歸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.09,0:19:40.14,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她母親呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.47,0:19:46.39,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美潮一家是住在國境東邊的比南但多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.40,0:19:48.00,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.01,0:19:52.00,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，就是那個被看不見的死神眷顧的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.80,0:19:55.49,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後，兩個人來到錫斯的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.69,0:19:59.76,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她母親已經病狀很明顯，餘日不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.14,0:20:04.36,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.11,0:20:08.85,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再給你梳頭了，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:10.98,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後呢…之後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.15,0:20:16.34,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓最珍惜美潮的人來幫你梳頭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.79,0:20:20.32,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弓奈姐姐幫我梳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.75,0:20:28.62,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:34.83,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算重要的人離開了，自己痛苦的要死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:39.97,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也要活下去，堅強的活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.31,0:20:45.06,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種堅強雖然非常悲傷，卻也十分可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.90,0:20:51.84,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.78,0:20:53.78,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.13,0:21:07.57,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都已經洗完澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.06,0:21:09.78,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，我馬上就去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.69,0:21:15.19,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很累的樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:19.79,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩，本來不想洗頭的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.29,0:21:21.72,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是今天發生了太多事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.93,0:21:23.18,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,係係係
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.31,0:21:26.48,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩，我來幫你擦乾頭髮吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:29.07,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直很想摸一摸…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.69,0:21:36.04,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是沒買海豚啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.36,0:21:39.18,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原以為你會買那個獎勵自己
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.63,0:21:45.51,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨旺前輩相信命運嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.15,0:21:47.58,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了，突然問這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.35,0:21:52.95,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說，今天遇到了讓我有這個想法的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.32,0:21:56.79,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給自己的獎勵，那個已經足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.06,0:22:00.70,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不信命運
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.92,0:22:05.01,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭一開始就甚麼都被決定、被授予
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.15,0:22:09.04,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是… 也是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.08,0:22:19.86,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某個人孕育出的偶然也許會在輾轉之間改變別人的人生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.64,0:22:26.95,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那就是命運的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.17,0:22:31.03,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.19,0:22:39.37,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D降調
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.84,0:22:49.63,Sora Eng dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來前輩今天也過得很美好呢
